HOME CHEFS, DUAL DOOR-IN-DOOR™ IS DESIGNED FOR YOU. AND FOR THE FAMILY TO ENJOY, AS WELL.

Keeping your ingredients fresh is just as important as keeping your recipes. But condiments, chilled stocks, and others are more frequently-sought-for items that also need refrigeration. Into Cooking Space can go all your ingredients smart way. By keeping often-used items on the door-end of Dual Door-in-Door™ storage space, you no longer have to worry about cold air loss for the rest of stored items. LG’s signature Dual Door-in-Door™ design feature is for home chefs, for sure, but also for the convenience of the rest of the family. We all have our favorite fridge items — drinks, snacks, mustard, and parmesan — which accumulate the cold air loss, affecting the freshness of the rest of the items in the fridge. No more worries. By keeping family member’s favorite items on the door side of the Door-in-Door™ Family Space, everyone can enjoy everything inside fresher and longer.











Largest Veg Basket

Largest space of 21 ltrs.* that allows you to store more along with moist balance crisper that keeps your vegetables moist & fresh for long.(*Applicable on 215/235/270 ltrs.)











Smart Connect™

















Smart Diagnosis™ System


							Fast and Effective diagnosis for problems.
						













Spice box


							Keeps your exotic spices, condiments and nuts in a moisture-free condition .These special air tight containers , helps preserve their natural flavor and richness.
						














MOIST BALANCE CRISPER


						This is a special lattice-type box cover which maintains moisture at an optimum level. Moisture from stored food is evaporated and then condensed on the lattice, maintaining the correct balance of moisture in the box.
					



















