Trust Smart Home ACM-250 - Build-in halogen dimmer 250W
















 





































































Trust Smart Home ACM-250 - Build-in halogen dimmer 250W




Trust Smart Home ACM-250 - Build-in halogen dimmer (trailing edge) with 6 memory addresses, developed for 230V and 12V halogen lighting with electronic transformer. Suited to dim lighting wirelessly with a Trust Smart Home transmitter of your choice. Simple installation in a junction or installation box. Maximum load 250 Watt or 220VA when connected to an electronic transformer. 





