Description
Applications
Specifications
Package contents
Product Questions
Downloads


 Details

The Trust Smart Home ACM-250 build-in halogen dimmer is developed to dim halogen lighting, in particular 12V halogen lighting with an electronic transformer. 
The maximum load of the Trust Smart Home ACM-250 is 250 Watt or 220VA when connected to an electronic transformer. 
The receiver can easily be installed in an existing (wall or ceiling) installation box or in closets. You can use a Trust Smart Home transmitter of your choice to dim the lights. 
The receiver has an electronic memory with 6 memory addresses, which means you can use up to 6 different Trust Smart Home transmitters to control the receiver. If you want to install this product outdoors, you can use the waterproof junction box.
This dim receiver is perfect to use with regular 230V halogen lighting, Eco Halogen lighting and 12V halogen lighting with an electronic transformer. 

 Details

 








Model  ACM-250Code System  AutomaticChannels  NoMemory addresses  6RF reception range  NoDetection angle  NoWater resistance  NoSequences  NoPercentage dimming  NoDusk/dawn function  NoPower Supply  AC 220V/50HzSuitable for Incandescent, Eco halogen, Halogen 230V, Halogen 12V with dimmable electronic transformer, Dimensions  53 x 53 x 21 mmWarranty  2 year carry-in 



