Key features



Desktop solution with wired keyboard and wireless mouse for a clean desk and optimal freedom
Full 360 degree radio technology operation. Transmits through almost any object.
Includes 19 extra programmable direct access keys for both multimedia and Internet functions
Direct access keys can be customized for your own personal requirements
Ergonomically designed 3 button wireless programmable dual scroll mouse
Including keyboard palmrest for comfortable typing
Mouse receiver integrated in keyboard







